ose our painters, you will know that you are in trusted hands.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); transition: all 0.3s ease-out 0s; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">To schedule an appointment, give us a call now. <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><a href=\"tel:7622185701\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-transform: capitalize; text-decoration-line: none !important;\">(762) 218-5701</a></strong></p>', 'uploads/serviceateampainting169809083311.jpg', '', 0, 'house-painting', 1, '2023-10-24 01:23:53', '2023-10-25 14:18:57');
